        <h2>Did You Know?</h2>
    <div id="trivia" class="txt-block">
        <h4>Trivia</h4>
<a href="/name/nm0680983?ref_=tt_trv_trv">Ellen Page</a> was the only choice to play Sylvia Likens.        <a href="trivia?ref_=tt_trv_trv"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>
                <hr />
     <div id="goofs"  class="txt-block">
        <h4>Goofs</h4>
Marlboro &quot;Blue Pack&quot; ( formerly known as &quot;Milds&quot;) cigarettes can be seen behind the counter of the convenience store. This variety did not exist until 1999.        <a href="trivia?tab=gf&ref_=tt_trv_gf"
class="nobr" >See more</a>  &raquo;
    </div>   
                <hr />
